Version 0.4.0 [Released January 19 2016]

* Refocus on core functionality
  * Remove inject_script_tag()
  * Remove :contains_zip_file
  * Remove destroy_unpacked()

* Make compat with ruby 1.8.7
  * Modify tooling 
    * Remove superfluous bin scripts
    * Remove superfluous version file
    * Remove $LOAD_PATH mangling
    * Remove bundler rake tasks
    * Remove minitest reporters
    * Remove byebug, pry and bundler
    * Make rubygems work under ruby 1.8.7
    * Add gemspec for ruby 1.8.7
  * Refactor HTML5ZipFile::File (remove rubyzip & improve interface)
    * Replace rubyzip with posix-spawn / 'unzip'
    * Add :size_packed
    * Rename :contents_size to :size_unpacked
    * Rename :entry_count to :entries
    * Rename :file_count to :file_entries
    * Rename :directory_count to :directory_entries
    * Remove :contains_zip_file
    * Hide constructor
    * Improve exceptions

* Add doctests

* Add kitchen sink example

* Set up CI
